	<a class="external-link" target="_blank" href="http://resolver.sub.uni-goettingen.de/purl?GDZPPN002336715">Link zum Preprint</a></p><div class="entry-details hide details-305"><i class="fa fa-times-circle"></i><h3><span class="pubTitel">Lower Eigenvalue Estimates for Dirac Operators</span></h3><h4>Autoren: Christian Bär
			(1992)
